song_lyrics: Loh mānīne tame sparshyā o pāras
Maune ghaṇu ghaṇu kahī gayā tame... 2
Chhe nathī nathī chhe na ramvī ramato
Ā charaṇe tamārā badhu lahī gayā ame... 3
Have to ame tame tame amenā ‘darshan’
Tame tame nā vaheṇmā vahī gayā ame... 4
title: Nathī ḍoḷvo avḍā’paṇno sāgar
